### The Incrementality Advantage

```
Service Business Attribution Challenge:
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

Ruler Analytics shows: Google Ads drives 40% of calls
But is that accurate?

mbuzz Approach:
├── Run geo holdout on Google Ads
├── 50% of markets: no Google Ads
├── 50% of markets: normal spend
├── Measure: actual call volume difference
├── Result: 25% actual lift (not 40%)
├── Conclusion: MTA overcredits Google by 60%
└── Reallocate budget with confidence
```

### Best For

- Service businesses wanting validated attribution
- Teams skeptical of MTA accuracy
- Companies ready to run experiments
- Those needing advanced attribution modeling

