## 2. CallRail — Best for Call Tracking Depth

**Why consider CallRail:** If call tracking is your primary need with lighter attribution requirements, CallRail is the specialist.

### CallRail vs Ruler Analytics

| Factor | Ruler Analytics | CallRail |
|--------|-----------------|----------|
| Call tracking depth | Good | ★★★★★ |
| Call recording | ✓ Yes | ✓ Yes |
| Call transcription | Limited | ✓ AI-powered |
| Conversation intelligence | Limited | ✓ Advanced |
| Marketing attribution | ★★★★☆ | ★★★☆☆ |
| Starting price | £349/mo | ~$40/mo |

### Why CallRail Over Ruler Analytics

CallRail goes deeper on call intelligence—AI transcription, keyword spotting, conversation analytics. If understanding what happens on calls matters as much as attributing them, CallRail excels.

### Best For

- Call-heavy businesses (agencies, home services, healthcare)
- Teams wanting call conversation intelligence
- Those with lighter attribution needs
- Budget-conscious (lower starting price)

